-- England’s Lampard to Miss Soccer’s Euro 2012 With Thigh Injury
-- B y   B o b   B e n s c h
-- 2012-05-31T16:52:42Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-31/england-s-lampard-to-miss-soccer-s-euro-2012-with-thigh-injury.html
England midfielder Frank Lampard will
miss the European soccer championship with a thigh injury, the
Football Association said on its website.  Chelsea’s Lampard was injured yesterday in training and
ruled out of the tournament following a scan today. Liverpool’s
 Jordan Henderson  will replace him in the squad, pending approval
from UEFA’s medical team, the F.A. said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bob Bensch at 
 bbensch@bloomberg.net  